data.name: Label1.Text
data.value: 1. 6 rows and 15 columns of grass boxes. 2. One bomb per column, randomly placed. 3. Player must click one box in the current column. 4. If correct, move to the next column and multiply reward. 5. If bomb is clicked — game over. 6. Player can also cash out early. (Note: One Box is mandatory before cashout).
